alma.scheduling.planning_mode_sim.define
Interface HasMembers

All Superinterfaces:
ArchiveEntity
All Known Implementing Classes:
SUnit, SUnitSet
public interface HasMembers
extends ArchiveEntity

The HasMembers interface is a collection of methods that must be implemented by all objects that belong to a project that can themselves contain members. Such objects must define and implement their own methods to add members.
